  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/7559641/" class="title-link">藏在名画背后的故事</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-7559641"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/59881801/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img1.doubanio.com/icon/u59881801-7.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/59881801/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">斑点紫罗兰</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2015-08-04"
      class="main-meta">2015-08-04 21:08:47</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_7559641_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  一幅幅精美的名画放在你的面前时，你会欣赏吗？他们都是谁，他们有怎样的故事呢？原来没有仔细看过希腊故事，但是因为《名画之谜：希腊神话篇》让我更多地认识他们。  作者中野京子，专攻德国文学、西方文化史。本书是艺术与文化的结合，在欣赏“美”的同时，更多了解希腊神话...

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/7559641/#comments">(5回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">4有用 / 1没用</span>
                  </div>
